cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with lidar datasets and their applications in surface reconstruction, object detection, and visualization, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new geometric descriptor for point cloud classification, which falls under the category of geometric reasoning (cs.GR). The use of machine learning methods for classification also suggests that the paper could be classified under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses the potential for filtering and improving visual understanding, which could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL).
